 VNet (vnet-demo)
 Two Subnets
1. Subnet 1 (subnet-public) – Public & Private Networking

VM1 (BIRD & BGP Router)
NIC 1 (Primary, Public IP) → External Traffic
NIC 2 (Secondary, Private IP) → Internal BGP Routing
ASN: 65516
2. Subnet 2 (subnet-private) – Private Network Only

VM2 (K3s Node)
1 NIC (Private IP Only)
